column5: Holy crackers, thought Barry was gonna force a tap but Lavar recovered and threw some seriously heavy knees and hammers at Barry who just crumpled from the barrage.  Hoping Miller gets the win over Diaz.
Go Diaz. Not sure why barry gave up the full mount. Lavar is a joke on the ground
Awesome. I bet on Belcher. Pretty sweet odds. All palhares has is leg locks

yeah, Nate has mad skills so hopefully a good fight. Belcher ? Gotta say I  was worried when he started playing footsie with Palhares but what an amazing ground game they had going on. Helluva finish. So far, great finishes tonight even though they're all first rounders.
